originalText.text: Truly have enjoyed working with Zack Mangel. It was by far my smartest career choice. WhiteCap and Zack have taken their time in assessing my biggest strengths, skills and how to best leverage my years of work experience. I admit it I was skeptical at first as I had never worked with a temp agency prior, however, looking back i wish I had worked with Zack sooner. I appreciate him checking in to assure my goals and the company's goals continue to align in addition to him not hesitating to be my advocate. He took the time to find a company that best aligned with my values and career goals. And I've already recommended him to previous colleagues of mine. I also love the company I work with and they have been extremely vocal of transitioning me to permanent.

originalText.text:
I had an amazing experience with White Cap. Gabriel Castillo was my recruiter. He was like my guardian angel, he helped me tremendously, especially to prepare for job interviews. He always was by my side every step of the way in the firm, from my job transition to when the firm offered me to work permanently with them.Gabriel was always respectful, super professional and attentive
answering my questions. My colleagues told me that they also had very good experiences with White Cap and their recruiters.

originalText.text: I had a great experience working with White Cap but all because of my recruiter Gillian Suzzan! Gillian has been nothing short of the best in terms of making sure I found the best fit. Social work is a very broad field and I definitely tend to be picky with my priorities, yet she stuck with me through the long process and she found the absolute perfect spot that I could not be happier about! Gillian was very attentive to my needs and consistently checks in to this day- even months later - to make sure that I'm still content with where I'm at and that my career goals are being met.

originalText.text: My experience with WhiteCap was a great one. Gabe Castillo has been detailed with all information and always available to answer my many questions. I was able to obtain an offer for full-time employment pretty quickly from the contract position through the agency and Gabe has been there every step of the way. I would definitely recommend Gabe and WhiteCap.
